pages.text:
Membership Benefits
Play 36 holes of the #1 designed golf course in central florida (Highlands Ridge) and one of the most scenic Audubon style courses (Preserve at Highlands Ridge)
Members receive preferred tee times at both golf courses all year long
No monthly food or beverage minimums
10% discount in golf shops at both courses
Exceptional service, our loyal golf members always come first.
5 free transferable golf rounds ($350 value) for every golf membership paying by November 1st.
